      <div class="msgContentFrame">You should think twice when buying new equipment. I skipped Tortoiseshell hora because of the rare repair materials needed. Unlike Spike Knuckles, which require a single iron nugget and I can get them repaired pretty quickly. If you are sticking to SP parties and are constantly at the helm of new equips, expect your repairs to come slowly. Crafters much catch up with the curve. </div>
